HEADWORD: Marginally
<hw>Mar"gin*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In the margin
of a book.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In a <er>marginal</er>{3} manner; barely
